      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Miscellaneous",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "SAC Weeks called from New Orleans on the matter discussed in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "attached teletype. He wanted to know what policy the Bureau was following",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "in connection with reports concerning these \"flying discs\" which were being",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "received.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "I told Mr. Weeks that, unless advised to the contrary, he should, in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "particular case at hand, allow G-2 to handle and not take any jurisdiction for the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "FBI. He was told the Bureau would be interested in being kept advised of develop-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "ments, and in copies of the photographs he said G-2 would make of the object",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "found, but that he should not allow himself to be jockeyed into a position where",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "investigative responsibility, if any were entailed, would fall on us. Mr. Weeks said",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "he would so handle unless I called him back immediately with instructions for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "specific action.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "As you will recall, I called you concerning the foregoing.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "RECORDED",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
